A cyberpunk scene showing a glowing holographic control panel floating in mid-air, with intricate nested translucent layers and geometric shapes folding and unfolding like origami. Each layer pulses with neon blue and electric purple circuits. A pair of hands wearing fingerless gloves manipulates the hovering interface, rearranging modular components that snap together seamlessly. The background features a rain-slicked cityscape with towering dark buildings reflecting the panel's glow. Steam rises from vents below, catching the light. The atmosphere is moody with deep shadows contrasting against the vibrant digital elements, suggesting the satisfaction of elegant technical solutions replacing crude workarounds.
